bicester rugby club is an english rugby union club situated in bicester town; 10 miles away from oxford. the club competes from the under 7 age up to the under 12's (minis), from the under 13's to the under 18 colts (juniors) and then from their very own 3rd xv to bicester's 1st xv, which participates in southern counties north. both bicester's juniors and seniors play at the bicester rugby club ground located on oxford street whilst the bicester mini rugby club is located at the bicester sports association (bsa) ground on akeman street, chesterton, only 5 minutes from the main bicester rugby ground.